main_body:
Every application for the right to import lodged in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 1143/98 shall be granted to the following extent:
(a) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(a) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 39,727 % of the quantities imported during the period 1 July 1999 to 30 June 2002;
(b) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 5,384 % of the quantities applied for.
